high_descs: Turn right and go straight, turn right and make a turn left head walk then turn left towards the dining table
Pick up banana from the dining table
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left then take a right then head straight, turn left towards the fridge
Place banana inside the fridge and then take it out.
Turn right and go straight, turn left towards the sink
anns.task_desc: Cooling the banana and placing it on the sink

high_descs: Turn right, at the end of the wall, turn right, at the end of the wall, turn left. Go forward, pass the table, turn right, go forward, turn left, approach the dining table.
Turn around. Go forward, turn right. When you reach the wall, turn left. Go forward, at the end of the wall, turn right, turn left. Reach the fridge, turn left.
Open the fridge, place the banana in the first level of the fridge. Close the fridge for 8 seconds. Close the fridge.
Turn right, continue forward to the middle of the sink cabinet.
Place the banana to the left of the sink cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Find the banana, cool it and take it to the sink cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the dining table.
Take the banana from the dining table.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the banana into the fridge.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the banana on the sink table.
anns.task_desc: Placed the banana on the sink table.
